		h1 TabNavigator
		p.container 
			| The 
			a(href='/api/#{latest.version}/symbols/ch.TabNavigator.html') TabNavigator
			|  component is a member of the 
			a(href='/api/symbols/ch.Controllers.html') Controllers
			|  family. It helps you organize and present large content. 
			| The component has views: the horizontal view and vertical view. 
		p.container 
			| The 
			a(href='/api/symbols/ch.TabNavigator.html') TabNavigator
			|  has three important parts:
		ul 
			li 
				| The 
				strong tablist
				|  is a list of links each pointing to the content. 
			li 
				| The 
				strong tabpanel
				|  is the container of the one part of the content. 
			li 
				| The 
				strong tabs
				|  is the group of the tabpanels. 
		p.container 
